data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom rambler in coveted Granite Lane Community where homes don't come on the market very often. .86-acre lot. 12x20 shop with 10x20 lean-to. Covered back deck to enjoy beautiful but finnicky Northwest weather year around. The roof is 1 year old. recently painted inside and out. Heat pump and furnace replaced about 3 years ago. Idyllic tree lined street leads to quiet cul de sac with great neighbors. Chehalis School District. Just minutes to freeway.
